'''Echo Lake''' was a [[lake]] on the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Tasariq]]. It was located in the center of the [[Mining/Legends|mining]] boom-town [[Roaring Crater]]. Echo Lake provided [[Oxygen/Legends|oxygen]] for the crater, and was stocked with [[Fish/Legends|fish]] by the owner of the nearby [[Lakefresh Restaurant]]. [[Fishing/Legends|Fishing]] was forbidden but licenses could be purchased from the [[Restaurant/Legends|restaurant]].<ref name="J15" />

